parameters.description: Intrinsic COTS per-capita growth rate (baseline reproduction). Higher values allow faster booms when conditions are favorable.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Intrinsic per-capita COTS population growth rate

parameters.description: Background adult COTS mortality rate.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Background adult COTS mortality rate per year

parameters.description: Conversion efficiency of consumed coral cover into the recruitment buffer that later contributes to adult COTS (captures energetic/eggs-to-adults effects with a one-year maturation delay).
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Efficiency converting consumed coral to recruitment buffer (adults accrue after delay)

parameters.description: Fraction of last year's recruitment buffer that matures into the adult COTS population this year (aggregates larval survival, settlement, and one-year maturation).
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: One-year maturation fraction from recruitment buffer to adults

parameters.description: Baseline (food-independent) COTS carrying capacity.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Baseline COTS carrying capacity without coral food

parameters.description: Increase in COTS carrying capacity per % coral food (weighted by wF and wS).
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Increase in COTS carrying capacity per coral cover %

parameters.description: Attack rate on fast corals (Acropora) in a multi-prey Type II response. Larger values increase selective predation on Acropora.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Attack rate on fast-growing Acropora corals

parameters.description: Attack rate on slow corals (Faviidae/Porites) in a multi-prey Type II response.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Attack rate on slow-growing Faviidae/Porites corals

parameters.description: Handling time for fast coral prey. Larger values reduce per-capita feeding at high prey cover via saturation.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Handling time per fast coral prey item (years)

parameters.description: Handling time for slow coral prey.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Handling time per slow coral prey item (years)

parameters.description: Intrinsic growth rate of fast-growing corals (Acropora).
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Intrinsic growth rate of fast-growing Acropora corals

parameters.description: Intrinsic growth rate of slow-growing corals (Faviidae/Porites).
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Intrinsic growth rate of slow-growing Faviidae/Porites corals

parameters.description: Effective maximum live coral cover for logistic growth terms (shared carrying capacity proxy for available substrate/habitat).
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Maximum total coral cover carrying capacity (%)

parameters.description: Competition coefficient: effect of slow corals on the carrying capacity experienced by fast corals.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Competition effect of slow corals on fast coral capacity

parameters.description: Competition coefficient: effect of fast corals on the carrying capacity experienced by slow corals.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Competition effect of fast corals on slow coral capacity

parameters.description: Maximum additional bleaching mortality rate for fast corals as SST exceeds the bleaching threshold.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Max bleaching mortality rate for fast corals (year⁻¹)

parameters.description: Maximum additional bleaching mortality rate for slow corals as SST exceeds the bleaching threshold (generally lower than fast corals).
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Max bleaching mortality rate for slow corals (year⁻¹)

parameters.description: SST threshold for the onset of bleaching mortality ramp for corals.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Sea surface temperature threshold for coral bleaching (°C)

parameters.description: Width (smoothness) of bleaching mortality ramp; larger values make the transition more gradual.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Smoothness width of bleaching mortality ramp (°C)

parameters.description: Thermal optimum for COTS reproduction/survival modifier.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Optimal temperature for COTS reproduction/survival (°C)

parameters.description: Thermal niche width (standard deviation) for the COTS temperature response.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Thermal niche width (std dev) for COTS temperature response (°C)

parameters.description: Saturating coefficient linking coral food availability to COTS reproduction (1 - exp(-beta_food * food_index)).
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Food saturation coefficient for COTS reproduction

parameters.description: Allee-like smooth threshold for COTS reproduction; below this, reproduction is limited.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Allee threshold for COTS reproduction limitation (individuals/m²)

parameters.description: Steepness of the Allee logistic function controlling low-density limitation strength.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Steepness of Allee effect logistic function

parameters.description: Adult-equivalent addition per unit larval immigration, modified by temperature and food availability.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Adult-equivalent scaling per larval immigration rate

parameters.description: Weight of fast-growing coral (Acropora) in the food index perceived by COTS.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Weight of fast coral in COTS food availability index

parameters.description: Weight of slow-growing corals in the food index perceived by COTS (lower reflects preference for Acropora).
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Weight of slow coral in COTS food availability index

parameters.description: Log of COTS observation standard deviation for lognormal likelihood; value corresponds to sigma ≈ 0.5 with a smooth minimum enforced.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log of COTS observation error standard deviation

parameters.description: Log precision for Beta likelihood of fast coral proportion; phi = exp(value) + phi_min with phi_min = 5.
parameters.enhanced_semantic_description: Log precision for Beta likelihood of fast coral cover

parameters.description: Log precision for Beta likelihood of slow coral proportion; phi = exp(value) + phi_min with phi_min = 5.
